  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed roof extension would be harmful to the appearance of the property and the conservation area in which it is situated and would disrupt the unaltered roofline of this section of the terrace. It would fail to respect the principles laid out in section 2.4.2 of the statutory Urban Design Guide (2006) and the provisions of the Conservation Area Design Guidelines. The proposal would conflict with Policies D1 (Overall Design), D4 (Designing in Context), D11 (Alterations and Extensions), D19 (Conservation Areas), D22 (New Development) and D42 (Buildings on the Local List) of the Islington Unitary Development Plan (2002)."
